<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Lalpa'n A hun Sam</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thihna thim nuoi a um in,
 Thagau sangtam amang zing;
 Hukdampana Aw, Hukdamna helo in,
 Hinna lampi mansakin, Thingbul suongbul aho ui,
 Ei haw guola tatdawk sa ahiu.

[V2]
 Hukdamna Chanchinpha,
 Gamtina phuongzak dingin;
 Lalpa'n tuhin ahun sam,
 A hun sam ahun sam zing,
 Hukdamna huongah lun puilut un.

[V3]
 2. Lalpa'n A hun hehpih a,
 Nanga dingin a hung thuok;
 Na gitloh leibat haw ahun ditsak,
 Gamthima Lalpa hehpih Thagau sang tam amang zing,
 Amau pui ding kuomah aum puoi.

[V4]
 3. Amauhaw chu pui dingin,
 Suohpih bang dinga nang muong ?
 Hun a chawma ni a liem zing ngala,
 Na leibat na dit loh leh Lal kawmah bang na gen die ?
 Tu hi Hukdam theih na ni ahi.

[V5]
 4. Lalpa kei ka um hila,
 Na hehpih te pui dingin;
 Na deih bang taka nei mat di'n ka nuom,
 Nang a ding in hing ka ting nanga ding mah in thing ka,
 Ka theihna ka pum in ei mang in.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>290</hymn_number>
</song>